etups seem to already work without it. I should think more about Docker and native image considerations too.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Assessing setup requirements**\\n\\nI'm considering whether the necessary setup counts before meaningful coverage is reachable. It's important for the native run to pass, though it doesn't directly relate to coverage reachability. The existing scaffold had a version 5.0.0, and I need to ensure compatibility with 5.0.1, which uses Netty 4.2.2.Final. I also have to clarify that no Docker is necessary. I'll make sure the guidance includes details on testing with an in-process Vert.x HttpServer and necessary runtime args for Java 25 native tests.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Vert.x Web Client can be meaningfully exercised with an in-process Vert.x HTTP server and no Docker or extra required Maven dependency, but version 5.0.1 still resolves Netty 4.2.2.Final and needs the same Java 25 native-run system properties already used for 5.0.0.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use local test setup: create a Vertx instance, start an in-process HttpServer on 127.0.0.1 with an ephemeral port, create WebClient/WebClientSession/CachingWebClient against it, and close WebClient, server, and Vertx in cleanup. Do not depend on public external HTTP services. For nativeTest on JDK 25/current-defaults, extend the existing runtime argument setup to 5.0.1 as well: add -Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"OAuth2WebClient references optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2 types; avoid OAuth2-specific coverage unless adding that optional dependency is intentionally in scope.\",\n    \"Native Image verification remains authoritative; the Netty/JDK 25 flags are advisory based on the resolved Netty 4.2.2.Final dependency and existing 5.0.0 setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05d7ed03a7a655ee016a40d530149c8194aa12ec50d4837d2c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2497, "output": 821, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30454, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782633763062, "responseId": "resp_05d7ed03a7a655ee016a40d523ab1081949fe4057500dd4f03"}, "toolResults": []}
